title: Does Apple Pay pose a threat to Canadian banks
text:
Does Apple Pay pose a threat to Canadian banks? 
Globe and Mail Saturday 24th October, 2015 
Apple Pay is expected to arrive in Canada before the end of the year, allowing Canadians to make small purchases up to $100 with their iPhones - but also delivering Apple Inc., the world's largest company by capitalization and most powerful brand, as a potential financial rival to the big banks.Should the banks be worried?
